    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/8c8d8ff2c49bdf2cfcfead74a1ee8387.avif?t=1771982235\" width=1560 height=296 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《阿卡迪亚的陨落》是一部角色扮演视觉小说，由你来塑造出自己想成为的样子。无论是做羞涩和事佬，大胆冒险者，还是不停开玩笑的捣蛋鬼，都由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演遭到一个犯了法的精灵附身的年轻见习炼金术士，猝不及防地卷入了人类与魔法的战争中，因而必须和一群非典型英雄结伴逃避各自的灾厄，顺利的话还能在旅途中拯救世界。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个不划分正确与错误选择的故事</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段没有坏结局的冒险之旅。你的决定不会阻止自己前进的步伐，但可能会影响在达到目标之前需要经受的考验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对话选项缀有语气标签。由你来选择角色是羞涩，大胆，还是在任何场合都开玩笑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你想成为炼金术大师，还是好好谈一场恋爱，又或者探索世界的奥妙，你的时间，你自己说了算。 </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色自定义&amp;成长</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仿照自己的外表，或者放飞幻想，创造出属于你的炼金术士形象。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由你来决定如何让创伤性事件塑造和发展你的角色个性。面对悲剧时，你会心怀仁慈，还是图谋报复？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/6bb733d52d08f2a61255260bb75902ef.poster.avif?t=1771982235\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/6bb733d52d08f2a61255260bb75902ef.webm?t=1771982235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/6bb733d52d08f2a61255260bb75902ef.mp4?t=1771982235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可攻略角色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与同伴们待在一起，培养深情厚谊，或者发展浪漫恋情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你来决定怎样与他人恋爱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对LGBTQ+群体友好</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/86223f1270181384a0178d279845485f.poster.avif?t=1771982235\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/86223f1270181384a0178d279845485f.webm?t=1771982235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/86223f1270181384a0178d279845485f.mp4?t=1771982235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途中会有五名同伴加入，你可以和其中四位发展出浪漫关系。无论是否谈恋爱，你都可以和每个人建立丰盈纯真的友谊，包括我们的第五位同伴麦姆，她完全做好了当你毕生挚友的准备！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >炼金术谜题</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用炼金术技能解除危机，帮助同伴，并改变周围的世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依靠炼金术技能和古老遗物的助力，与强大的恶魔较量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磨练技能以发现秘密配方。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/41da886a0e6090f12c14f26d62894828.poster.avif?t=1771982235\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/41da886a0e6090f12c14f26d62894828.webm?t=1771982235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174640/extras/41da886a0e6090f12c14f26d62894828.mp4?t=1771982235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
